{
  "texts": [
    "This integration facilitates the examination of interactions within complex scenarios, adhering to the demands of our computational simulations.",
    "An example of FCL's application in robotics is its integration with the PR2 robot, a mobile manipulation platform developed by Willow Garage [103].",
    "The PR2 robot, which is equipped with integrated stereo and laser sensors, utilizes FCL for executing complex tasks such as pick and place operations.",
    "FCL facilitates the robot's ability to generate collision-free paths through cluttered environments by conducting continuous collision detection queries, a critical component for effective grasp planning.",
    "Through the seamless execution of collision and proximity queries, FCL enables robots to navigate and interact with their environments in a safe and informed manner [102]."
  ]
}